46:03.678 --> 46:05.044
I'm not staying out here.

46:05.137 --> 46:07.720
I'm just going to get it. I'll be back.

46:09.433 --> 46:12.551
No, Jeff! Jeffery!

46:12.645 --> 46:14.477
Do you see him? I can't see him.

46:14.563 --> 46:16.725
Where'd he go? Jeffery!

46:16.816 --> 46:18.978
Jeffery, come back!

46:19.986 --> 46:22.069
Jeff. Do you see him?

46:23.906 --> 46:26.273
- Jeff!
- Are you okay?

46:26.367 --> 46:27.778
You okay, man?

46:27.868 --> 46:30.155
I thought I was going
to make it the whole way.

46:30.246 --> 46:32.078
Jeff, come back right now.

46:32.164 --> 46:33.496
Maybe just leave it, man.

46:33.582 --> 46:36.165
I'm almost there, guys. Just let me.

46:36.252 --> 46:38.164
- Jeff, come back!
- Jeff!

46:38.254 --> 46:41.588
Oh, shit. I can't see him anymore.

46:45.303 --> 46:46.293
What?

46:46.387 --> 46:48.174
- Jeff!
- Shit!

46:48.264 --> 46:49.721
- Jeff!
- Jeff, get out of there!

46:49.807 --> 46:52.345
- Jeff!
- Come back, man!

46:52.435 --> 46:54.222
Where is it, Josh? Where did it go?

46:54.312 --> 46:55.723
I don't know, I don't know, I don't know.

46:57.648 --> 46:59.139
Oh, sh it!

47:02.820 --> 47:06.734
- Jeff!
- Jeffrey! Jeffrey... Jeffrey!

47:16.375 --> 47:18.788
- It's okay, Megan.
- Oh, my God! Jeffrey!

47:28.804 --> 47:30.636
You son of a bitch!

47:30.723 --> 47:33.181
- Dude, I'm...
