48:17.228 --> 48:20.767
I know, I know. It's all right.
We can do it, Megan.

48:23.901 --> 48:25.392
I love you.

48:35.704 --> 48:37.411
Just turn the camera off, okay?

48:37.498 --> 48:40.662
