49:11.782 --> 49:14.525
Some kind of rescue.

49:14.618 --> 49:16.530
To me it looks like they're flying away.

49:18.080 --> 49:20.697
They don't... I think
they stop the rescues at night.

49:20.791 --> 49:23.033
