49:24.962 --> 49:25.952
It's...

49:26.046 --> 49:29.084
Guys, we just got to stay here where we are.

49:29.175 --> 49:33.044
Take care of each other. Get through it.

49:34.346 --> 49:35.553
Oh, it's so cold.

49:41.395 --> 49:44.012
What are you doing
