49:56.994 --> 49:58.360
- Shh...
- No, no, no. Oh, my God!

49:58.454 --> 49:59.820
- Jeffrey.
- It's okay, it's nothing.

49:59.914 --> 50:02.076
- Josh, what can you see, man?
- Straight ahead, man.

50:02.166 --> 50:03.282
There's something floating right...

50:03.375 --> 50:04.741
