50:04.835 --> 50:05.996
Wait, wait, wait. Jeff, Jeff, come back.

50:06.086 --> 50:07.748
- Grab it!
- Jeff, Jeff don't go too far. Jeff!

50:08.756 --> 50:09.872
Get it, man.

50:11.217 --> 50:13.755
- What is that?
- Bring it over here.

50:13.844 --> 50:16.086
Jeff, please be careful.

50:17.097 --> 50:18.929
Hey, man, I can't see you.

50:20.184 --> 50:21.595
- Did you get it?
- Jeff?

50:22.603 --> 50:23.559
Oh, sh it!

50:23.646 --> 50:25.763
- Jeff?
- Got it.

50:26.774 --> 50:28.060
I'm coming back.

50:29.610 --> 50:31.101
He's coming.

50:33.113 --> 50:36.026
- You shitting me?
- Oh, my God!

50:36.116 --> 50:37.357
- Really?
- Look at this thing.

50:37.451 --> 50:39.989
Oh, my God. Are you okay?

50:40.079 --> 50:41.365
