51:26.375 --> 51:27.911
Are you getting this, Josh?

51:29.128 --> 51:31.495
It's like a fucking bouncy castle.

51:33.799 --> 51:36.963
- Look!
- Whoa!

51:37.052 --> 51:39.886
- Oh, my God. We can climb in there.
- We have a castle.

51:41.307 --> 51:44.095
All right. What do you think?

51:44.184 --> 51:46.892
- Get up in there, man.
