01:02:29.287 --> 01:02:31.199
- Stop splashing.
- Don't touch me right now.

01:02:31.289 --> 01:02:33.872
- Okay, just get off.
- You're going to fucking attract sharks.

01:02:33.959 --> 01:02:36.747
- You're the frickin' liar, okay?
- What?

